  <section id="submission-protocol">
    <h2>Submission Protocol</h2>
    <p>Interested individuals should send the application by email to: <strong>sas2016submission@ntu.edu.sg</strong>. Please include the following <span class="highlight">3 separate files</span>:</p>

    <h4>File 1 (Word or PDF):</h4>
    <ul>
