      <li>Email</li>
      <li>Twitter username (if you have one)</li>
      <li>Affiliation (if any)</li>
      <li>Title</li>
      <li>Bio (no more than 1000 characters)</li>
      <li>Whether you will be presenting as a <a href="#20-min-paper">20 min paper</a> or <a href="#5-min-talk">5 min Micro-talk</a>.</li>
